{
  "texts": [
    "We use the scipy and statsmodel libraries for statistical tests in this paper.",
    "Propose your preferred object design: For the object you are assigned, you will first propose the design you prefer. a.",
    "To help you in this process, you will be shown several different designs for that object and will be asked to select the designs you like, based on the room shown. b.",
    "You will then use the selected object designs to propose your preferred design.",
    "E.g., if you are assigned a chair, you will describe the type of the chair, the characteristics of the back, seat, arms and legs, color, and/or the type of material you prefer."
  ]
}